## 3. Authentication Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant APIGateway
    participant AuthService
    participant TokenService
    participant UserService
    participant TrustService
    participant Cache
    participant AuditService
    
    Client->>APIGateway: Request + JWT Token
    APIGateway->>AuthService: Validate Token
    
    AuthService->>Cache: Check Token Cache
    alt Token in Cache
        Cache-->>AuthService: Cached Token Data
    else Token Not Cached
        AuthService->>TokenService: Verify JWT Signature
        TokenService-->>AuthService: Signature Valid
        
        alt Signature Invalid
            AuthService-->>APIGateway: Invalid Token
            APIGateway-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
        else Signature Valid
            AuthService->>UserService: Get User Data
            UserService-->>AuthService: User Information
            
            AuthService->>TrustService: Get Trust Score
            TrustService-->>AuthService: Trust Score
            
            AuthService->>Cache: Cache Token Data
            Cache-->>AuthService: Cache Confirmed
        end
    end
    
    AuthService->>AuditService: Log Authentication Attempt
    AuditService-->>AuthService: Log Confirmed
    
    AuthService-->>APIGateway: Authentication Result
    
    alt Authentication Failed
        APIGateway-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    else Authentication Success
        APIGateway->>Client: Continue Processing
    end
```

