## 4. Error Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Error Occurred] --> B{Error Type}
    B -->|Validation Error| C[Client Error 4xx]
    B -->|Business Logic Error| C
    B -->|Permission Error| C
    B -->|System Error| D[Server Error 5xx]
    B -->|Database Error| D
    B -->|Network Error| D
    
    C --> E[Format Error Response]
    D --> F[Generate Error ID]
    
    F --> G[Log Full Error Details]
    G --> H[Sanitize Error for Client]
    H --> I[Check Error Sensitivity]
    
    I -->|Sensitive| J[Generic Error Message]
    I -->|Non-Sensitive| K[Detailed Error Message]
    
    J --> L[Create Error Response]
    K --> L
    
    E --> M{Development Environment?}
    L --> M
    
    M -->|Yes| N[Include Stack Trace]
    M -->|No| O[Minimal Error Info]
    
    N --> P[Return Error Response]
    O --> P
    
    P --> Q[Update Error Metrics]
    Q --> R[Alert if Critical]
    R --> S[Monitor Error Patterns]
```

