## 5. Recovery Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant APIGateway
    participant CircuitBreaker
    participant RetryService
    participant BusinessService
    participant HealthChecker
    participant Cache
    participant Monitoring
    
    Client->>APIGateway: Request
    APIGateway->>CircuitBreaker: Check Circuit State
    
    alt Circuit Open
        CircuitBreaker-->>APIGateway: Circuit Open
        APIGateway->>Cache: Try Fallback Cache
        alt Cache Hit
            Cache-->>APIGateway: Cached Response
            APIGateway-->>Client: Cached Response
        else Cache Miss
            APIGateway-->>Client: 503 Service Unavailable
        end
    else Circuit Closed
        CircuitBreaker-->>APIGateway: Circuit Closed
        APIGateway->>BusinessService: Process Request
        
        alt Service Failure
            BusinessService-->>APIGateway: Error Response
            APIGateway->>RetryService: Check Retry Policy
            
            alt Retry Allowed
                RetryService-->>APIGateway: Retry Permitted
                APIGateway->>BusinessService: Retry Request
                
                alt Retry Success
                    BusinessService-->>APIGateway: Success Response
                    APIGateway-->>Client: Success Response
                else Retry Failure
                    BusinessService-->>APIGateway: Error Response
                    APIGateway->>CircuitBreaker: Report Failure
                    CircuitBreaker->>CircuitBreaker: Update Failure Count
                    
                    alt Threshold Reached
                        CircuitBreaker->>CircuitBreaker: Open Circuit
                        APIGateway->>Client: 503 Service Unavailable
                    else Below Threshold
                        APIGateway->>Client: 500 Internal Server Error
                    end
                end
            else No Retry
                RetryService-->>APIGateway: No Retry
                APIGateway-->>Client: 500 Internal Server Error
            end
        else Service Success
            BusinessService-->>APIGateway: Success Response
            APIGateway->>CircuitBreaker: Report Success
            CircuitBreaker->>CircuitBreaker: Reset Failure Count
            APIGateway-->>Client: Success Response
        end
    end
    
    APIGateway->>Monitoring: Update Health Metrics
    HealthChecker->>Monitoring: Periodic Health Check
```

