## 6. Moderation API Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Reporter
    participant ModerationAPI
    participant ValidationService
    participant QueueService
    participant Moderator
    participant NotificationService
    participant AuditService
    participant TrustService
    participant Database
    
    Reporter->>ModerationAPI: Submit Report
    ModerationAPI->>ValidationService: Validate Report
    
    alt Validation Failed
        ValidationService-->>ModerationAPI: Validation Errors
        ModerationAPI-->>Reporter: 400 Bad Request
    else Validation Success
        ModerationAPI->>Database: Save Report
        Database-->>ModerationAPI: Report Saved
        
        ModerationAPI->>QueueService: Queue for Review
        QueueService-->>ModerationAPI: Queued Successfully
        
        ModerationAPI->>AuditService: Log Report Creation
        AuditService-->>ModerationAPI: Log Confirmed
        
        ModerationAPI-->>Reporter: 202 Accepted + Report ID
        
        QueueService->>Moderator: Assign Report
        Moderator->>ModerationAPI: Start Review
        
        ModerationAPI->>Database: Get Report Details
        Database-->>ModerationAPI: Report Data
        
        Moderator->>ModerationAPI: Submit Decision
        ModerationAPI->>ValidationService: Validate Decision
        
        alt Decision Valid
            ValidationService-->>ModerationAPI: Decision Valid
            ModerationAPI->>Database: Update Report Status
            Database-->>ModerationAPI: Status Updated
            
            ModerationAPI->>TrustService: Update Trust Scores
            TrustService-->>ModerationAPI: Scores Updated
            
            ModerationAPI->>NotificationService: Notify Parties
            NotificationService-->>ModerationAPI: Notifications Sent
            
            ModerationAPI->>AuditService: Log Decision
            AuditService-->>ModerationAPI: Log Confirmed
            
            ModerationAPI-->>Moderator: Decision Processed
        else Decision Invalid
            ValidationService-->>ModerationAPI: Decision Errors
            ModerationAPI-->>Moderator: 400 Bad Request
        end
    end
```

