## 7. Content Creation API Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ContentAPI
    participant ValidationService
    participant TrustService
    participant ModerationService
    participant ContentService
    participant SearchService
    participant Cache
    participant Database
    participant NotificationService
    
    User->>ContentAPI: Create Content
    ContentAPI->>ValidationService: Validate Content
    
    alt Validation Failed
        ValidationService-->>ContentAPI: Validation Errors
        ContentAPI-->>User: 400 Bad Request
    else Validation Success
        ContentAPI->>TrustService: Check Trust Score
        TrustService-->>ContentAPI: Trust Score
        
        alt Trust Score Low
            TrustService-->>ContentAPI: Review Required
            ContentAPI->>ModerationService: Queue for Review
            ModerationService-->>ContentAPI: Queued
            
            ContentAPI->>Database: Save as Pending
            Database-->>ContentAPI: Content Saved
            
            ContentAPI->>User: 202 Accepted + Review Status
        else Trust Score High
            TrustService-->>ContentAPI: Auto-Approve
            ContentAPI->>ContentService: Process Content
            ContentService->>Database: Save Content
            Database-->>ContentService: Content Saved
            
            ContentService->>SearchService: Update Search Index
            SearchService-->>ContentService: Index Updated
            
            ContentService->>Cache: Update Cache
            Cache-->>ContentService: Cache Updated
            
            ContentService->>NotificationService: Notify Followers
            NotificationService-->>ContentService: Notifications Sent
            
            ContentService-->>ContentAPI: Content Published
            ContentAPI--->User: 201 Created + Content ID
        end
    end
```

