## 8. User Management API Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant UserAPI
    participant AuthService
    participant ValidationService
    participant UserService
    participant TrustService
    participant AuditService
    participant Database
    participant NotificationService
    
    Admin->>UserAPI: Update User Status
    UserAPI->>AuthService: Verify Admin Permissions
    AuthService-->>UserAPI: Admin Confirmed
    
    UserAPI->>ValidationService: Validate Update Request
    ValidationService-->>UserAPI: Validation Result
    
    alt Validation Failed
        UserAPI-->>Admin: 400 Bad Request
    else Validation Success
        UserAPI->>UserService: Get User Details
        UserService->>Database: Query User
        Database-->>UserService: User Data
        UserService-->>UserAPI: User Details
        
        UserAPI->>TrustService: Calculate Trust Impact
        TrustService-->>UserAPI: Trust Impact
        
        UserAPI->>Database: Update User Status
        Database-->>UserAPI: Status Updated
        
        UserAPI->>AuthService: Update User Sessions
        AuthService-->>UserAPI: Sessions Updated
        
        UserAPI->>AuditService: Log Status Change
        AuditService-->>UserAPI: Log Confirmed
        
        UserAPI->>NotificationService: Notify User
        NotificationService-->>UserAPI: Notification Sent
        
        UserAPI-->>Admin: 200 OK + Updated Status
    end
```

